## Files to Create or Modify

* `comparison_document.md`: A markdown file containing the comparison document (300-800 words).
* `comparison_tables.md`: A markdown file containing any tables or charts created to illustrate the differences.
* `review_comment.md`: A markdown file containing the review comment posted on the issue.
* `review_comment_links.txt`: A text file containing the links to the RustChain repository and specific files, PRs, features, or doc sections reviewed.